Key Match Events: Nikola Jokic had 46 points and 10 rebounds, leading the Denver Nuggets to a 122-111 overtime victory over the San Antonio Spurs.
Post-Match Reflections: Victor Wembanyama finished with 20 points and 23 rebounds for San Antonio, but was scoreless and without a rebound in OT.
Miscellaneous Highlights: Wembanyama has 57 double-doubles in 101 career games.
